descriptionHtml:
Jasmin enb real cinema final 2



Instructions


1. First, go to http://enbdev.com/download_mod_tesskyrim.htm (ENB Site)
    Please, Download ENB v0.119    (d3d9.dll) 


2. First, go to http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/27043/     
    Please, Download Enhanced Lights and FX


3. RemoveAmbientInteriorFog.esp
    RevampedExteriorFog.esp
    Supreme Storms.esp
    Realistic Lighting Patcher.esp

    Delete please !




4. Realistic Lighting.esp / EnhancedLightsandFX.esp

   SkyrimLauncher -> Data Files -> check (active)

  





Letterbox effect originates from enbeffect.fx of \'hd6\', which is vignetting effect.

Jasmin ENB for the first time attempted and uploaded vignetting effect to the letterbox.

Letterbox is Jasmin\'s idea and thus please write a credit anyone who uploads and uses letterbox.

This is basic etiquette for who modify and upload ENB.
